      "title": "New Prime Minister Dinesh will be sworn in tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena is scheduled to take oath as the Prime Minister of the new government tomorrow (22) morning.",
        "Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena is sworn in as Prime Minister in front of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena currently serves as the Speaker of the Parliament."
      ],
